title: Kiss Man Dark Skin Tone Woman Light Skin Tone
description: Illustrates a man and a woman kissing, with diverse skin tones. This emoji represents romantic relationships, love, and affection between heterosexual couples, highlighting skin tone variations.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this emoji captures a tender kiss between a man with a dark skin tone and a woman with a light skin tone, both rendered with Apple’s signature smooth gradients and realistic lighting. Their faces are depicted with soft, rounded edges, conveying a gentle and affectionate moment with a warm, rosy blush. This couple kissing emoji, as seen on Apple devices, symbolizes romance, deep connection, and the joy of shared intimacy, perfect for expressing heartfelt feelings in your digital conversations.
